    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[0]'
      value: "O sya salamat \u2018nak, gusto lamang kita kamustahin at kausapin,
        pwede ka na ulit makipaglaro sa mga apo ko."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[1]'
      value: Kung gusto mong makipag-usap muli sa akin, hanapin mo ako malapit sa
        mga bintana sa caida, talagang pinahahalagahan ko ang kumpanya. Sana nga
        lang di maalikabok ang mga bintana.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[2]'
      value: Kung maalikabok po pwede ko naman linisin.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[3]'
      value: "Sigurado ka \u2018nak ayaw naman kita iabala, bata ka pa, dapat naglalaro
        ka."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[4]'
      value: Sigurado po ako Nang, Pasasalamat ko narin to sa pagtanggap sa akin
        sa iyong tahanan.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[5]'
      value: Kay bait mo naman na bata, maraming salamat nak.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[6]'
      value: Nanang notices your staring and begins to address your confusion.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[7]'
      value: Nakakatulong siya pang alis ng mga Apido, habang nagdidilig ka.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[8]'
      value: "Ah, she\u2019s making an excuse. Although slightly true as smoke helps
        keep away bugs, either way it's not my place to question her habits. It's
        best to start watering her plants."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[9]'
      value: Buti na lang at nahanap ko, baka maapakan pa ni Dodong tapos masira
        pa to.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: _CurrentSpeakers.Array.size
      value: 6
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[10]'
      value: "hala ba\u2019t ako?"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[11]'
      value: "The sisters started laughing at your joke, you take this as a good
        sign that you\u2019re getting along with them well."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[12]'
      value: "Haha buti nga\u2026 regalo pa naman sa akin to ni Tita Concha nung
        pinanganak ako. Kaya mahalaga to sa akin."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[13]'
      value: "\u201CKaya mag ingat ka kasi, nag aalala ka masyado sa mga kapatid
        mo nakalimutan mo na sarili mo."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[14]'
      value: "You realize too late that your reply wasn\u2019t something a ten year
        old would probably say, especially towards someone who\u2019s older than
        them. Carmen looks at you with a confused face."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[15]'
      value: "Sigurado ka bang mas bata ka sa akin? Ba\u2019t ang tanda mo kung magsalita?"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[16]'
      value: I almost messed up my cover, I managed to get away the first time but
        Carmen is starting to become suspicious this time.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[17]'
      value: I should think of a reply to minimize the suspicion.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[18]'
      value: As the kids begin their studies and activities you take this time to
        roam around the sala and observe some of the decorations and furinture all
        across the room.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[19]'
      value: A few minutes later, Ima Tina comes into the living room to check on
        you and the kids.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[20]'
      value: Oh kamusta mga anak?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[21]'
      value: Hello Ima!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[22]'
      value: Ima smiles at the greeting and then turns to her children one by one
        to see how they were doing before turning to you.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[23]'
      value: Oh ikaw anak kamusta ka na?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[24]'
      value: Mabuti naman po, magkakasundo naman po kami..
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[25]'
      value: Aba mabuti naman.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[26]'
      value: Nga lang pwede ba kitangiabala?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[27]'
      value: pwede mo bang bisitahin si Nanang, hinihintay ka niya sa terasa sa labas
        ng cosina, gusto ka niya daw kamustahin.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[28]'
      value: Nanang? If you recall correctly Nanang meant Grandmother, and here Nanang
        was the main head of the household.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[29]'
      value: According to your family, Nanang had passed only a few years after the
        Raymundo house was built, so it's a surprise and a small relief that you
        made it into a timeline where you get to meet her.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentSpeakers.Array.data[0]'
      value: Nanang
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentSpeakers.Array.data[1]'
      value: Nanang
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
